@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Privacy Policy";
}

<div class="container mt-5">
    <h1 class="display-5">Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="mt-3">
        At School Management System, we are committed to protecting the privacy and confidentiality of all users, including students, instructors, and administrators.
    </p>

    <h4 class="mt-4">1. Data Collection</h4>
    <p>
        We collect only the necessary information required to manage student records, course data, and enrollment details within the CMS.
        This includes names, emails, course information, and system activity.
    </p>

    <h4 class="mt-4">2. How We Use Your Data</h4>
    <ul>
        <li>To manage student registration and course enrollment</li>
        <li>To display and update academic information securely</li>
        <li>To improve the user experience within the CMS</li>
    </ul>

    <h4 class="mt-4">3. Data Security</h4>
    <p>
        All information is stored securely using encrypted connections and role-based access. We take every precaution to prevent unauthorized access or disclosure.
    </p>

    <h4 class="mt-4">4. No Third-Party Sharing</h4>
    <p>
        We do not share any user data with third-party services or organizations. All data remains confidential and is used solely within the system.
    </p>

    <h4 class="mt-4">5. Changes to This Policy</h4>
    <p>
        This policy may be updated as the system evolves. Any changes will be clearly communicated on this page.
    </p>

    <p class="mt-4">
        If you have any questions or concerns about this privacy policy, please contact the system administrator.
    </p>
</div>